----------------DB Locations table-----------------
id_country
id_region
child_count

Find top cities each country, mark them in the DB.

--------------Locales---------------
In header display a select to choose the locale.

We will try to detect the locale from the browser. Once a locale is selected we keep it as cookie.

Anywhere in the site can pass as paramenter ?locale=es_ES

All the other actions will be filtered by the locale chosed.


-------------------API-----------------------
They accept parameter locale! and parameter chained, if chained set only return ID:name

/api/countries.json
/api/regions.json?country=IDCOUNTRY
/api/cities.json?region=IDREGION OR ?country=IDCOUNTRY only_top = 1



